https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=2640629789347426&amp;id=124616407615456\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.facebook.com%2Fstory.php%3Fstory_fbid%3D2640629789347426%26id%3D124616407615456&d=%2BaoNGjxKkOyNIKnkVXg3cUXxRC0ARC%2FjKSdqd%2FiyNcw%3D&h=caebd044\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=2640629789347426&amp;id=124616407615456</a><br />\n<br />\nPost：<a href=\"https://lih.kg/eDEkrT\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/eDEkrT</a><br />\n<br />\n//平等機會婦女聯席發言人區美寶稱，3個組織11月初共同發起控訴警察性暴力的國際聯署，截至本月7日收集到21國共85個團體聯署支持。為了向聯合國專家展開更有力游說，3個組織呼籲受害者主動聯絡他們並接受訪談，強調會保密。//<br />\n<br />\n我們現正收集抗爭者在抗爭期間／被捕後遭受警察性暴力對待的資料，作以下用途：<br />\n1. 協助受害人可以完整保留該事件之紀錄<br />\n2. 整理資料並製成 #ProtestToo 實錄，以作追究之用<br />\n3. 收集國際聯署（進行中），結合個案提交聯合國，爭取國際間關注及支持<br />\n4. 要求香港政府獨立、公正地徹查「反送中運動」發生的性暴力<br />\n<br />\n*個人資料及通訊紀錄在實錄完成後可按受訪者意願全部銷毀<br />\n詳情及相關安排請聯絡Tg @protesttoo"},{"pid":"73aa2ba76dce3e099093066fcede6dda47514f31","tid":1777080,"uid":54564,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-10T09:09:37.000Z","msg":"一開始話拉11人<br />\n之後話有「屠龍小隊」成員<br />\n今日就話連「v小隊」成員都有份<br />\n<br />\n下次仲有咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b5acf39eebac237c6be088e6e9d9ac2207f0581e","tid":1777080,"uid":8768,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b10ed8ed190f3188b688c62337ed313e32e1129c","tid":1777080,"uid":22436,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-10T08:50:46.000Z","msg":"流浮山刀手仲同v小隊打緊杖 班記者唔好up得就up<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-10T09:11:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ff095635ad0a05b92b2a40b4e473d817613a1288","tid":1777080,"uid":188482,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-10T09:12:57.000Z","msg":"寫個個覺唔覺得on9<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgm